# Title: Discovery Using AzureHound
# Author: Janantha Marasinghe
# Date: 2022-11-27
# Level: high
# Description: Detects AzureHound (A BloodHound data collector for Microsoft Azure) activity via the default User-Agent that is used during its operation after successful authentication.
# MITRE Tactic: Discovery
# Tags: attack.discovery, attack.t1087.004, attack.t1526
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/cloud/azure/signin_logs/azure_ad_azurehound_discovery.yml

ResultType=0 userAgent="*azurehound*"